      <title>加拿大育空地区计划重新开放其从维多利亚黄金公司查封的矿山</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/canada-s-yukon-aims-to-reopen-mine-it-seized-from-victoria-gold</link>
